snippet.title: National Domestic Violence Hotline
snippet.description: For nearly twenty five years, the National Domestic Violence Hotline has answered the call – over 5 million calls, chats, and texts to date – for those affected by relationship abuse. The only 24/7/365 national service provider offering service via call, chats and texts, we work to shine a light on the hidden epidemic of domestic violence, supporting and advocating for survivors, providing hope in times of crisis, and promoting health relationships for all.
